Package: soh
Type: Package
Title: Hotspot analysis and stability metrics
Version: 0.2
Date: 2017-02-06
Author: Viliam Simko, Julian Bruns
LazyData: yes
Imports:
  raster,
  methods,
  dplyr,
  scales
Suggests:
  knitr,
  testthat
Maintainer: Viliam Simko <viliam.simko@gmail.com>
Description: Hotspot analysis and stability metrics. This package provides the
  standard Getis-Ord G* statistics applied to raster data and also a modified
  Focal Getis-Ord which is more stable in terms of finding hotspots.
